readme:
Service Usage

This service is used to send images and additional details captured by SmartGate to HADOOP to be stored.

Service Behaviour

SmartGates capture images, device details and image details and sends call to HADOOP. HADOOP stores images against the BiometricImageIdentifier that was provided by SmartGate. HADOOP sends acknowledgement in response.
ImageType and ImageUsageType have been made mandatory due to the filters in SV288 Retrieve Image Identifiers Request. ImageFormatType has been made mandatory due to the same madatory field in SV150 RetrievePersonImageResponse
